== Biography
- I am currently a PhD candidate in the [http://www.ie.cuhk.edu.hk/ Department of Information Engineering],  
[http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/ The Chinese University of Hong Kong] 
\n advised by [http://staff.ie.cuhk.edu.hk/~mhchen Prof. Minghua Chen]. 
- I received my BEng degree from the [http://ee.sjtu.edu.cn/ Department of Electronic Engineering], [http://www.sjtu.edu.cn Shanghai Jiao Tong University] in 2012. 
- From May 2015 to October 2015, I was a visiting scholar at  
[https://engineering.purdue.edu/ECE School of Electrical and Computer Engineering], [http://www.purdue.edu/ Purdue University]
\n advised by [https://engineering.purdue.edu/~chihw/ Prof. Chih-Chun Wang].

